    uint256 bal = balances[msg.sender];
    require(bal > 0);
    balances[msg.sender] = 0;  // effect before interaction
    (bool ok, ) = msg.sender.call{value: bal}("");
    require(ok);
}
```
Or use a `nonReentrant` guard on *all* state-modifying functions.

